{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/LuckyPennySoftware/AutoMapper/issues/25","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/LuckyPennySoftware/AutoMapper","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/LuckyPennySoftware/AutoMapper/issues/25/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/LuckyPennySoftware/AutoMapper/issues/25/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/LuckyPennySoftware/AutoMapper/issues/25/events","html_url":"https://github.com/LuckyPennySoftware/AutoMapper/issues/25","id":724936,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWU3MjQ5MzY=","number":25,"title":"make projected sourceMember accessible in PropertyMap","user":{"login":"h0lg","id":680296,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjY4MDI5Ng==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/680296?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/h0lg","html_url":"https://github.com/h0lg","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/h0lg/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/h0lg/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/h0lg/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/h0lg/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/h0lg/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/h0lg/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/h0lg/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/h0lg/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/h0lg/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[],"state":"closed","locked":true,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":4,"created_at":"2011-04-01T17:49:19Z","updated_at":"2019-05-09T00:46:21Z","closed_at":"2011-04-04T08:48:06Z","author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","type":null,"active_lock_reason":"resolved","sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"Hey Jimmy,\n\nI am currently adding a feature to [FluentMetadata](https://github.com/DerAlbertCom/FluentMetadata) on [this fork](https://github.com/forger/FluentMetadata/tree/feature/copyMetadataFromAutomappedProperties).\nBesides defining metadata in a fluent syntax, FluentMetadata is a framework for reusing the metadata of models for view models and OR-mappings.\nThe feature I'm working on uses the mapping information provided by AutoMapper to copy metadata from one mapped type to the other.\n\n_Now, where's the problem?_\n\nWell, the way AutoMapper implements the projection of properties there's no clean way I know of to access the source property of a mapping like\n\n<pre>\nMapper.CreateMap<Source, Destination>()\n    .ForMember(destination => destination.RenamedMember, o => o.MapFrom(source => source.NamedMember));\n</pre>\n\nMy suggestion is to make this sourceMember accessible making it possible to use the AutoMapper configuration as a source of information about how types map to each other and thus adding value to AutoMapper itsself.\nLooking into the source several possibilities of implementing this come to my mind:\n- adding a new (nullable?) property to PropertyMap exposing the source member, either as a Func<TSource, TMember> or as MemberInfo\n- making DelegateBasedResolver<TSource, TMember> and its readonly _method field public\n\nWhat do you think of this?\n\nKind regards, Holger\n","closed_by":{"login":"h0lg","id":680296,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjY4MDI5Ng==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/680296?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/h0lg","html_url":"https://github.com/h0lg","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/h0lg/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/h0lg/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/h0lg/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/h0lg/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/h0lg/subscriptions","organization